  "text": "The model consisted of an array of 50 Â 50 Â 50 unit cells. By putting potentials (often relatively artificial ones) on the atoms in the model and allowing the model to relax through MC simulation, local correlations were introduced. Fourier transform of the model then allowed comparison of the model diffraction pattern with the observed SCDS [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Similarly, the PDF of the model was calculated and compared with observations.",
